\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Bathos}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 An abrupt transition in style from the exalted to the commonplace, producing a ludicrous effect. While often unintended, bathos may be used deliberately to produce a humorous effect.[7][8]}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 The ballerina rose gracefully en pointe and extended one slender leg behind her, like a dog at a fire hydrant.[9]}
